messages.messageBody:
Hi All,

Thought I would pass along this info that I recently received since I did get emails from several people.
I should have mentioned previously that my daughter is 16.

Looking forward to meeting with you,
Annie


_______________________________________________________________________



Mountain Laurel Day
Sam's Point Preserve
Saturday, June 23rd
10:00 AM - 4:00 PM
Celebrate the beauty of the mountain laurel in peak splendor at Sam's Point Preserve.
Festivities scheduled throughout the day include photography and art workshops and hikes,
kid's activities, a botany hike to the Ice Caves, and a native plant sale!
Parking will be waived for all Wawarsing residents!!!
Please pre-register for hikes and activities.
***SEE ATTACHMENT FOR A SCHEDULE OF EVENTS***
